{"id":1924,"date":"2021-11-02T19:09:44","date_gmt":"2021-11-02T18:09:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?p=1924"},"modified":"2021-11-02T19:09:45","modified_gmt":"2021-11-02T18:09:45","slug":"become-an-early-tester-of-the-gotriple-beta-version","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/2021\/11\/become-an-early-tester-of-the-gotriple-beta-version\/","title":{"rendered":"Become an Early Tester of the GoTriple Beta Version!"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p>Are you interested in helping with the initial testing of the Beta version of the GoTriple platform?\u00a0 We currently offer different ways to do just that!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The TRIPLE project has partnered with another European H2020 project called <a href=\"https:\/\/www.reachout-project.eu\/\"><strong>ReachOut<\/strong><\/a> to recruit early testers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.reachout-project.eu\/\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Reachout_web-1024x362.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1927\" width=\"309\" height=\"109\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Reachout_web-1024x362.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Reachout_web-300x106.jpg 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Reachout_web-768x272.jpg 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Reachout_web.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 309px) 100vw, 309px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>ReachOut, the <strong>beta-testing campaign platform<\/strong> for research projects, is able to offer a 30 Euro reward for up to 24 participants for the testing of the Beta version of GoTriple via their website.\u00a0 Participants will be entered into a draw if more than this number fully complete the test. Testing will take less than an hour with a short questionnaire to complete at the end to tell us what you think of the platform so far and what should be improved.\u00a0\u00a0To start the testing, please use this link: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.reachout-project.eu\/view\/Main\/#TRIPLE_anc\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.reachout-project.eu\/view\/Main\/#TRIPLE_anc<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Beta version of GoTriple is an initial release of some of the planned features of GoTriple. More features of GoTriple are still to come, such as the user profiles and relevant discovery dashboards. So stay in touch to find out more on <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/<\/a> . We will likely run another testing session\u00a0before Christmas, as soon as additional features are released.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are also looking for some participants for the <strong>qualitative testing phase<\/strong> and for the definition of the governance of GoTriple. For any questions about the ReachOut testing campaign or to participate in the qualitative research, please get in touch with <a href=\"mailto:p.forbes@abertay.ac.uk\">p.forbes@abertay.ac.uk<\/a> or <a href=\"mailto:s.depaoli@abertay.ac.uk\">s.depaoli@abertay.ac.uk<\/a>\u00a0and subscribe to the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/triple-community-mailing-list\/\" target=\"_blank\">TRIPLE Community Mailing List<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another, very simple way to give feedback on GoTriple is to click on the <strong>&#8220;bug button&#8221;<\/strong> on the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\">platform website<\/a> and complete a short form:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"77\" height=\"72\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/GoTriple-bugbutton-screenshot2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1925\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get involved and give us your opinion on how we can make GoTriple better!!<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Are you interested in helping with the initial testing of the Beta version of the GoTriple platform?\u00a0 We currently offer different ways to do just that! The TRIPLE project has partnered with another European H2020 project called ReachOut to recruit<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1930,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[23,22,8,7],"tags":[13,5],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1924"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1924"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1924\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1931,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1924\/revisions\/1931"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1930"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1924"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1924"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1924"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}